SHADOWRUN 5E - MECHANICS REFERENCE: OLUSTHRA
--------------------------- MAGIC & DRAIN ---------------------------
DRAIN POOL: 13 (WIL 6 + CHA 7)
MAGIC LIMIT: 6 (Base) | 9 (With Power Focus Active)
TRADITION: Shamanic (Raven Mentor)

BONUSES:
• Power Focus (Rating 3): +3 to ALL Magic Tests (Casting, Summoning, Counterspelling)
• Raven Mentor: +2 Manipulation Spells | +2 Con (Deception)
• Focused Concentration (5): Can sustain ONE spell up to Force 5 with NO -2 penalty.

--------------------------- DICE POOLS -----------------------------
SORCERY (MAG 6 + Focus 3 = 9 Base)
• Spellcasting (Manipulation): 17 (Skill 6 + Focus 3 + Spec 2 + Raven 2 + MAG 6)
• Spellcasting (Illusion/Health): 15 (Skill 6 + Focus 3 + MAG 6)
• Counterspelling: 12 [BASE] | Detection Spec: 14
• Ritual Spellcasting: 15 [BASE] | Spell Spec: 17

CONJURING (MAG 6 + Focus 3 = 9 Base)
• Summoning: 15 [BASE] | Spirit of Man Spec: 17
• Banishing/Binding: 15 (Focus 3 + MAG 6 + Skill)

SOCIAL & PERCEPTION
• Con (Deception): 18 (CHA 7 + Skill 6 + Spec 2 + Raven 2 + First Impression?)
• Intimidation: 11 (CHA 7 + Skill 4)
• Perception: 11 (INT 5 + Skill 6)

--------------------------- SPELL QUICK-REF ------------------------
[FORMULA: F = Force of Spell | D = Drain Result]

MANIPULATION (Pool: 17 | Limit: 9)
• Control Thoughts: [F-2] (Complex, Opposed: Spell + MAG [9] vs. WIL + INT)
• Levitate: [F-1] (Physical, Target: 200kg per net hit)
• Magic Fingers: [F-1] (Physical, AGI/STR = Net Hits)
• Trid Phantasm: [F-1] (Realistic, Multi-sense)

ILLUSION/HEALTH (Pool: 15 | Limit: 9)
• Improved Invisibility: [F-1] (Sense: Visual, Resistance: INT+CHA)
• Physical Mask: [F-1] (Sense: All, Resistance: INT+CHA)
• Heal: [F-4] (Essence check; Net hits = boxes healed; Drain Min: 2)

--------------------------- DERIVED STATS --------------------------
INITIATIVE: 8 + 1d6 (REA 3 + INT 5)
DODGE: 8 (REA 6 + INT 3)
SOAK: 12 (Body 2 + Lined Coat 9 + Helmet 1)
COMPOSURE: 13 (WIL 6 + CHA 7)
JUDGE INTENTIONS: 12 (INT 5 + CHA 7)

LIMITS:
• Physical: 3
• Mental: 5
• Social: 8

--------------------------- CASTING FLOW ---------------------------

DECLARE FORCE: Choose F (Usually 1–6).

Note: If F > MAG (6), Drain is Physical.

CAST: Roll Pool vs. Target Resistance or Threshold.

LIMITS: Hits are capped by Force or Magic Limit (9).

DRAIN: Roll 13 dice vs. Spell Drain Value (e.g., F-2).

-------------------------- SPIRIT TRADITION ------------------------
Raven Shamans perceive spirits as urban tricksters or feathered echoes.
• Combat: Beast
• Detection: Water
• Health: Earth
• Illusion: Air
• Manipulation: Man (Olusthra Specialization)

